Wow.&#xD;
&#xD;
This is a powdery sweet, yet juicy flavor with a bit of bite to it. As close as i can describe it...imagine a martini with flat 7-up as the body, and an equal mixture of tequila and vodka adding in the boozy sting, with the rim dusted with confectioners sugar. And that dab of koolada just ads a hint of chil and a little extra sting. I rather like it!
